hypermedea-lib 0.3 API

Packages 
Package Description
org.hypermedea
Main Hypermedea package (includes artifacts to be used by hypermedia agents).
org.hypermedea.json
Wrapper classes for agents to handle JSON values (used by the ThingArtifact).
org.hypermedea.ld
Classes related to Hypermedea's Linked Data crawler (used by the LinkedDataArtifact).
org.hypermedea.owl
Classes related to Hypermedea's ontology artifact (used by the OntologyArtifact).
org.hypermedea.pddl
Wrapper classes for definitions in PDDL, the Planning Domain Definition Language (used by the PlannerArtifact).
org.hypermedea.pddl.planners  
org.hypermedea.tools
Miscellaneous tools used across artifacts.
